175 A.3d 162 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. STEPHEN HERNANDEZ, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-285 September Term 2017

079492 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004705-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
